THE GROUP

The Hair Masters Group, founded in 2013, operates 20 salons. The group has presence PAN India and is also engaged in health and restaurant industry.

Hair Masters Luxury Salon

Hair Masters today is synonymous with providing the right blend of service, luxury and quiet efficiency. It is domestically acclaimed for all-round excellence and unparalleled levels of rejuvenating & reviving salon services.

A distinctive feature of The Groups salons is their highly motivated and well trained staff that provides exceptionally attentive, personalized and warm service. The Groups luxury salons have established a reputation for redefining the paradigm of luxury and excellence in service amongst salons around the country.

Hair Masters Luxury Salon

The Groups commitment to excellence, attention to detail and personalized service has ensured a loyal list of guests and accolades in salon industry. Recognizing the importance of quality training in salon services & management, The Hair Masters Group has established The Hair Masters Academy in New Delhi. Today, this institution is considered amongst the best in country with approximately 100 students graduating each year.
